Liberty Phoenix https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liberty_Phoenix 0 Liberty Mariposa Phoenix (née Bottom; born July 5, 1976) is an American former child actress. She is the older sister of Summer Phoenix and younger sister of River Phoenix, Rain Phoenix, and Joaquin Phoenix.
